      "message": "but all weights are the same? because each commit has equal chance of getting picked\n\nin my mental model there a decision tree. First we pick a commit with P\u003d1/commits. Then in that commit, pick a file.\nlike this https://www.mathsisfun.com/data/probability-tree-diagrams.html\nis this traditional probability?",
